    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Offering a sophisticated balance of luxury and durability, it represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver. Experience the assurance of quality engineering and a well-preserved driving experience.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your weekend adventures or the daily commute. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it runs like a dream! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable car that won\u2019t let you down, this is the one. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 1995 BMW M3, featuring the venerable S50 3.0L inline-six with crisp VANOS engagement and linear power delivery. This driver-focused example retains its factory-spec Getrag 5-speed manual transmission and 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and reinforced rear subframe mounting points, mitigating common E36 floor pan fatigue. Recent service includes a complete cooling system overhaul and valve adjustment. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the lateral dynamics and throttle response remain razor-sharp, making it an ideal candidate for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Reliable used vehicle. Mechanically sound. Good interior and exterior condition. Clean title. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior finish still catches the light beautifully, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the driver-side door\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, and it has never been smoked in. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It features a complete service history with recent oil and filter changes, a new engine air filter, and a cooling system flush performed within the last six months. It handles predictably and cruises quietly at highway speeds. This is a solid, honest car that needs nothing but a new driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and long-term value. This motorcar has been curated to ensure mechanical reliability and features a well-appointed interior that reflects a history of attentive care. Having passed our comprehensive multi-point inspection, it stands as a testament to enduring quality and sophisticated engineering. This is an exceptional opportunity for the professional seeking a dependable and prestigious driving experience without compromise.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and ready for its next adventure! I've taken great care of it, so it's running smoothly and looks great too. If you're looking for a dependable ride that's perfect for daily commutes or weekend trips, this is the one for you. It\u2019s been a great companion to me, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much. Can't wait for it to find a new home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. The chassis has been addressed with a subframe reinforcement kit to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Equipped with a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. While the finish shows light patina typical of a well-maintained driver, the mechanical vitals are excellent, following a recent valve adjustment and fluid service. A purist-grade specimen optimized for performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
